title: Fascinating Transitions: Friday, October 28th, 2022
description:
1. Tom Brady and Gisele Bundchen to File for Divorce After 13 Years of Marriage (PEOPLE) (11:55)
  2. 'Let the good times roll!' Elon Musk takes over at Twitter (Daily Mail) (20:42)

  4. 'Bachelor in Paradise' alum Joe Amabiule marries Serena Pitt in courthouse wedding (Page Six) (30:42)
  5. Harry Hamlin and daughter Delilah disturb fans with 'creep,' 'provocative' photo (Page Six) (35:28)
